## Open Items (Warfighter Pilot Blockers)

These must be resolved before any warfighter pilot contract is signed:

- [ ] **CAC/PIV Auth** — Current Supabase Auth is appropriate for OEM product only. Warfighter pilot may require CAC/PIV, DoD SSO, or IL-compliant auth. Must be scoped before pilot begins. See `CONSTRAINTS_DATA_SECURITY.md`.
- [ ] **Data Classification** — Determine what classification level DoD operational data carries and whether it can legally reside on commercial cloud. See `CONSTRAINTS_DATA_SECURITY.md`.
- [ ] **Cached Data Policies** — Not yet defined. Must be resolved before warfighter pilot. See `CONSTRAINTS_DATA_SECURITY.md`.
